525
00:33:24,919 --> 00:33:27,672
Find another girl to play the fool.

526
00:33:29,173 --> 00:33:31,467
Okay, just 30 seconds?

527
00:33:33,761 --> 00:33:34,679
[clears throat]

528
00:33:35,847 --> 00:33:37,056
Ready?

529
00:33:37,765 --> 00:33:41,102
Timer starts now.

530
00:33:41,185 --> 00:33:43,229
I'm desperate. I didn't tell you,

531
00:33:43,312 --> 00:33:45,606
but if I do get my inheritance,
I will help not just you,

532
00:33:45,690 --> 00:33:46,733
but your family as well.

533
00:33:46,816 --> 00:33:48,276
Please let me impregnate you.

534
00:33:48,359 --> 00:33:50,403
I don't want to do this
with anyone else but you.

535
00:33:50,486 --> 00:33:53,865
