no one would dare court you.

536
00:33:53,948 --> 00:33:56,159
Who would want to court a pregnant woman?

537
00:33:56,242 --> 00:34:01,414
But I promise
I'll spoil you when you give birth.

538
00:34:01,497 --> 00:34:04,667
