will be all over you

539
00:34:04,751 --> 00:34:06,961
but when they get to know you,
they'll love you.

540
00:34:07,045 --> 00:34:10,256
Even a gay like me would like you
if I weren't gay.

541
00:34:10,339 --> 00:34:13,968
So please let me impregnate you
so we can have kids--

542
00:34:14,052 --> 00:34:15,136
Stop!

543
