550
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:45,833
[Chiqui] Bell-ya?

551
00:34:47,001 --> 00:34:49,670
Idiot. Bella!

552
00:34:49,754 --> 00:34:51,672
"Bell-ya"? Bella Flores?

553
00:34:51,756 --> 00:34:53,800
[Chiqui] But I don't get it.

554
00:34:55,843 --> 00:34:57,970
Who are you, anyway?
Who am I supposed to be?

555
00:34:58,054 --> 00:35:00,139
Why are we wearing these?

556
00:35:01,516 --> 00:35:04,101
You are Edward Cullen.

557
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:06,604
You're a vampire.

558
00:35:07,897 --> 00:35:11,234
I am Bella Swan. A goddess.

559
00:35:12,193 --> 00:35:16,614
We need to role-play to get me going.

560
00:35:16,697 --> 00:35:17,615
Know what I mean?

561
00:35:17,698 --> 00:35:19,242
All right.

562
00:35:19,325 --> 00:35:22,578
Twilight is my favorite movie.

563
00:35:22,662 --> 00:35:24,455
-Okay?
-Mmm.

564
00:35:24,539 --> 00:35:28,376
Oh, here.
Shine the light on your face. [gasps]

565
00:35:31,170 --> 00:35:32,088
Edward...

566
00:35:33,631 --> 00:35:35,174
you're turning me on.

567
00:35:35,258 --> 00:35:37,844
I'm getting turned on, Edward.

568
00:35:38,886 --> 00:35:40,721
How can you get turned on? I look dead.

569
00:35:40,805 --> 00:35:44,308
Dead people turn you on?
I think you should see a doctor.

570
00:35:44,392 --> 00:35:46,727
You talk too much. Stop complaining.

571
00:35:48,062 --> 00:35:50,314
Just say your lines.

572
00:35:50,398 --> 00:35:53,943
You can ad-lib if you wish,
as long as in the end,

573
00:35:54,026 --> 00:35:57,363
um, you bite me, okay?

574
00:35:57,446 --> 00:35:58,364
Okay.

575
00:35:58,447 --> 00:36:00,491
Is that clear, Edward?

576
00:36:01,659 --> 00:36:03,286
Is that clear, Edward?

577
00:36:03,369 --> 00:36:05,204
Tell me, Bella...

578
00:36:05,288 --> 00:36:06,956
Bella, tell me... wait.

579
00:36:07,039 --> 00:36:09,041
Why are they speaking in our language?

580
00:36:09,750 --> 00:36:13,087
Stop ruining the moment. Just go on.

581
00:36:13,170 --> 00:36:15,006
-So what if it's our language?
-Okay, okay.

582
00:36:15,089 --> 00:36:16,591
Go on, continue!

583
00:36:17,341 --> 00:36:19,051
[breathing deeply] Bella...

584
00:36:19,135 --> 00:36:21,971
What am I? What am I?

585
00:36:22,054 --> 00:36:24,265
You are a vampire.

586
00:36:24,348 --> 00:36:28,477
Rawr! Rawr!

587
00:36:29,228 --> 00:36:31,188
Idiot!

588
00:36:31,272 --> 00:36:32,982
It's Twilight, not The Lion King.

589
00:36:34,233 --> 00:36:36,861
-Fine. Okay.
-Again!

590
00:36:37,778 --> 00:36:41,282
Bella, aren't you afraid of me?

591
00:36:41,866 --> 00:36:43,784
I'm not afraid of you, Edward.

592
00:36:43,868 --> 00:36:46,120
You should be scared of me.

593
00:36:46,204 --> 00:36:47,830
I'm not, Edward.

594
00:36:47,914 --> 00:36:51,542
My only fear is
if you are no longer with me.

595
00:36:52,627 --> 00:36:53,836
[moans]

596
00:37:00,885 --> 00:37:03,137
-[growls]
-[laughs]

597
