That hurts!

598
00:37:09,894 --> 00:37:11,354
Ouch! Ouch!

599
00:37:12,730 --> 00:37:14,523
[screams]

600
00:37:15,191 --> 00:37:17,777
-Chiqui, what have you done?
-Samuel, sorry.

601
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:19,445
But you did tell me to bite you.

602
00:37:19,528 --> 00:37:21,948
I told you to bite me, not kill me!

603
00:37:29,121 --> 00:37:30,831
[Kat] How's it coming along?

604
00:37:30,915 --> 00:37:32,625
Will you be done soon?

605
00:37:32,708 --> 00:37:34,961
I might fall asleep.

606
00:37:35,044 --> 00:37:37,171
Hey! Don't sleep!

607
00:37:37,255 --> 00:37:38,881
I'm really making an effort here.

608
00:37:38,965 --> 00:37:42,885
Do you think this is easy for me?

609
00:37:42,969 --> 00:37:45,221
This isn't easy for me, either.

610
00:37:45,304 --> 00:37:46,847
This gay.

611
00:37:46,931 --> 00:37:48,474
Just make yourself comfortable.

612
00:37:48,557 --> 00:37:50,685
I'll come out right away, okay?

613
00:37:50,768 --> 00:37:52,603
When I'm ready.

614
00:37:57,942 --> 00:37:59,318
Gabbi!

615
00:38:00,945 --> 00:38:02,113
What is it again?

616
00:38:02,196 --> 00:38:05,241
Let's grab a bite!

617
00:38:05,324 --> 00:38:08,077
You know I'm concentrating.
Don't bother me.

618
00:38:09,120 --> 00:38:10,454
Fine.

619
00:38:17,211 --> 00:38:19,088
Hold on.

620
00:38:19,171 --> 00:38:21,424
