621
00:38:21,507 --> 00:38:23,843
They're asking if we will extend our stay.

622
00:38:23,926 --> 00:38:25,428
Isn't it obvious?

623
00:38:26,137 --> 00:38:28,264
So quick-tempered!

624
00:38:28,347 --> 00:38:31,851
Uh, yes, we will extend our stay.

625
00:38:33,436 --> 00:38:35,604
No. Make it two more days.

626
00:38:36,772 --> 00:38:37,940
[Gabriel] Kat!

627
00:38:39,358 --> 00:38:42,820
Kat! Are you ready? Assume the position!

628
00:38:43,362 --> 00:38:45,281
[exclaims] I've been ready.

629
00:38:45,865 --> 00:38:48,409
Gabbi! Shocks!

630
00:38:48,492 --> 00:38:50,911
I don't think I can look at you.

631
00:38:51,037 --> 00:38:52,413
I might throw up.

632
00:38:53,039 --> 00:38:55,166
The feeling is mutual.

633
00:38:55,666 --> 00:38:57,126
Quick! Are you ready?

634
00:38:57,209 --> 00:39:00,421
I'm not going to face you, okay?
Just do your thing.

635
00:39:00,504 --> 00:39:02,506
Yes, I can do it. Quick!

636
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:04,008
-Go!
-[Gabriel] Game?

637
00:39:04,091 --> 00:39:04,925
Go!

638
00:39:05,009 --> 00:39:07,803
[Gabriel screams]

639
00:39:07,887 --> 00:39:09,305
[laughs nervously]

640
00:39:09,930 --> 00:39:12,600
-[Gabriel giggling]
-[Kat screams]

641
00:39:20,775 --> 00:39:24,028
Success! I'm going to have a baby.

642
00:39:24,111 --> 00:39:26,155
