instead of the entrance!

646
00:39:32,953 --> 00:39:36,082
You didn't check first.

647
00:39:36,916 --> 00:39:38,834
You're driving me crazy!

648
00:39:38,918 --> 00:39:40,878
So, sorry, no baby?

649
00:39:40,961 --> 00:39:43,339
-Don't count on it!
-Sorry.

650
00:39:43,422 --> 00:39:44,673
Haggard!

651
00:39:54,058 --> 00:39:56,644
-[man shouting] Joy!
-[knocking on door]

652
00:39:57,478 --> 00:39:59,230
-[shouting] Joy!
-[door opens]

653
00:39:59,897 --> 00:40:02,400
I've been here for ages!

654
00:40:02,483 --> 00:40:04,026
Out of my way!

655
00:40:04,110 --> 00:40:06,570
[man] Come here. Make me a cup of coffee!

656
00:40:09,073 --> 00:40:10,074
[man shouting] Joy!

657
00:40:10,157 --> 00:40:11,117
[door closes]

658
00:40:46,819 --> 00:40:50,322
Mmm. How did it go?

659
00:40:52,992 --> 00:40:54,702
I tried meeting women in a bar.

660
00:40:56,245 --> 00:40:57,288
And?

661
00:40:58,497 --> 00:41:00,332
Epic fail.

662
00:41:05,296 --> 00:41:07,673
I'm sure you'll come up with a plan.

663
00:41:10,259 --> 00:41:12,011
Whatever that will be,

664
00:41:12,970 --> 00:41:14,513
you have my support.

665
00:41:16,765 --> 00:41:19,101
But keep in mind, Dane.

666
00:41:19,935 --> 00:41:24,148
We don't need a huge amount of money.

667
00:41:24,648 --> 00:41:27,568
-[glass breaking in distance]
-[Joy faintly] Have pity on me!

668
00:41:27,651 --> 00:41:30,446
-[Joy crying] I'm pregnant!
-[man] I don't care!

669
00:41:30,529 --> 00:41:32,364
She's pregnant?

670
00:41:32,448 --> 00:41:34,408
And that jerk continues to hound her?

671
00:41:35,492 --> 00:41:38,245
Babe, women should protect each other.

672
00:41:38,329 --> 00:41:41,540
It's been a long time since I practiced
my tae kwon do skills. Okay?

673
00:41:41,624 --> 00:41:43,709
It's not that... Dane! Dane!

674
00:41:43,792 --> 00:41:46,879
-[Joy crying]
-No, not that, Dane. Dane!

675
00:41:50,591 --> 00:41:52,051
[man] Stay out from this!

676
00:41:52,134 --> 00:41:53,969
-[Daniel] Stop that!
-Dane?

677
00:41:54,053 --> 00:41:55,596
-[man] Don't meddle with us!
-Dane!

678
00:41:56,263 --> 00:41:58,224
Don Emilio, this is Joy.

679
00:41:58,891 --> 00:42:01,936
-Hi, Uncle, may I eat?
-Of course.

680
00:42:02,019 --> 00:42:03,979
Join us. Sit down.

681
00:42:04,521 --> 00:42:07,191
Oh, this, then this, and this...

682
00:42:08,692 --> 00:42:12,112
-This one, and this...
-[clears throat] What a gobbler.

683
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,448
Did you say something?

684
00:42:14,532 --> 00:42:18,702
Mmm. I just said, "Maybe she wants rice."

685
00:42:18,786 --> 00:42:20,079
Rice? There's no rice.

686
00:42:20,162 --> 00:42:22,790
[muffled] Sorry, I'm very hungry.

687
00:42:23,874 --> 00:42:25,960
I'm eating for two.

688
00:42:26,919 --> 00:42:29,338
Joy's pregnant. I'm the father.

689
00:42:29,421 --> 00:42:32,341
[both laughing]

690
00:42:32,424 --> 00:42:34,385
You mean, I'm going to be a grandfather?

691
00:42:34,468 --> 00:42:35,803
Yes, Don Emilio.

692
00:42:35,886 --> 00:42:38,597
[Don Emilio laughing]

693
00:42:39,932 --> 00:42:43,686
Don Emilio... how can you be sure

694
00:42:43,769 --> 00:42:45,479
that he is the father of the child?

695
00:42:46,272 --> 00:42:48,274
How come we just met this girl?

696
00:42:49,191 --> 00:42:51,902
Unlike you guys, I wanted
to be sure before introducing her.

697
00:42:51,986 --> 00:42:53,779
Do you want to see the pregnancy test kit?

698
00:42:53,862 --> 00:42:55,447
A pregnancy test kit?

699
00:42:55,531 --> 00:42:56,699
That's crap.

700
00:42:57,241 --> 00:43:00,286
Who knows where you got that!

701
00:43:00,911 --> 00:43:03,497
[Gabriel] Listen to him,
he has a point, Don Emilio.

702
00:43:03,581 --> 00:43:05,749
Don't tell me you believe
everything Daniel says.

703
00:43:05,833 --> 00:43:07,668
He's a smooth liar.

704
00:43:07,751 --> 00:43:09,378
Take it from me.

705
00:43:09,461 --> 00:43:11,338
He has deceived me in the past.

706
00:43:11,422 --> 00:43:13,716
Well, well, well, why?

707
00:43:13,799 --> 00:43:17,970
Are you scared that I'll get
the 300,000,000 pesos?

708
00:43:18,053 --> 00:43:20,222
-Don't be so sure.
-Why would I be?

709
00:43:20,306 --> 00:43:25,728
[all bickering loudly]

710
00:43:25,811 --> 00:43:28,188
Silence, all of you!

711
00:43:31,650 --> 00:43:35,571
