712
00:43:36,405 --> 00:43:37,781
is at nine weeks.

713
00:43:39,450 --> 00:43:40,951
How far along is she?

714
00:43:42,286 --> 00:43:44,830
-A little over a month.
-Okay.

715
00:43:44,913 --> 00:43:47,166
After the first trimester,

716
00:43:47,249 --> 00:43:49,043
we will conduct a DNA test.

717
00:43:50,544 --> 00:43:51,920
In the meantime,

718
00:43:52,004 --> 00:43:54,423
let me enjoy my son's good news.

719
00:43:54,506 --> 00:43:55,799
Let's eat.

720
00:43:57,176 --> 00:44:00,554
[Daniel] Eat a lot,
so the baby won't starve.

721
00:44:00,637 --> 00:44:03,015
My birthday is coming up next month.

722
00:44:03,932 --> 00:44:06,018
My brother is throwing me
a surprise party,

723
00:44:06,727 --> 00:44:08,854
along with members of my fraternity.

724
00:44:08,937 --> 00:44:10,481
You call that a surprise?

725
00:44:11,106 --> 00:44:13,984
It's a surprise
because they don't know that I know.

726
00:44:15,486 --> 00:44:18,364
I will bring you all,
so my brothers will meet you.

727
00:44:18,447 --> 00:44:20,407
Bring your girlfriends,

728
00:44:20,491 --> 00:44:25,371
so they'll see
that I don't have gay children.

729
00:44:25,454 --> 00:44:28,457
But... haven't they always known?

730
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:30,876
It's all speculation. Gossip.

731
00:44:31,668 --> 00:44:33,420
Once a blind item on a gossip website.

732
00:44:33,504 --> 00:44:35,214
But no one has confirmed it.

733
00:44:36,673 --> 00:44:39,009
[both laughing]

734
00:44:39,093 --> 00:44:40,761
Stop it.

735
00:44:41,720 --> 00:44:44,264
-Let's do it here.
-Okay.

736
00:44:44,348 --> 00:44:46,684
-Vampire. Vampire.
-Yes!

737
00:44:46,767 --> 00:44:48,769
[both exclaiming and laughing]

738
00:44:49,728 --> 00:44:53,148
You look like a frog, not a vampire.

739
00:44:53,232 --> 00:44:54,692
Wait. Stay there.

740
00:44:54,775 --> 00:44:56,693
Let me strike a pose.

741
00:44:56,777 --> 00:44:59,321
There.

742
00:44:59,405 --> 00:45:00,697
Hold on.

743
00:45:01,615 --> 00:45:04,284
Hey, don't forget me!

744
00:45:04,368 --> 00:45:07,704
Estong is just an appetizer,
I'm still the main course!

745
00:45:08,372 --> 00:45:09,456
What a pest!

746
00:45:09,540 --> 00:45:10,749
Are you in a rush? Fine.

747
00:45:10,833 --> 00:45:12,835
-Get it over with!
-Fine!

748
00:45:12,918 --> 00:45:14,211
She's so...

749
00:45:14,294 --> 00:45:17,840
You, lie on the bed.

750
00:45:17,923 --> 00:45:19,800
-Come here, come here.
-That's it.

751
00:45:23,595 --> 00:45:25,222
Don't look at me. Cover your face.

752
00:45:25,305 --> 00:45:26,682
-Hurry.
-What?

753
00:45:26,765 --> 00:45:28,392
-[giggling] Go.
-Here it is.

754
00:45:31,728 --> 00:45:37,151
[Chiqui squealing and giggling]

755
00:45:37,234 --> 00:45:38,318
[coughing]

756
00:45:38,402 --> 00:45:41,405
Chiqui,
you sound like a pig being strangled.

757
00:45:41,488 --> 00:45:42,990
I'm just helping you get in the mood.

758
00:45:43,073 --> 00:45:44,992
You can't be the only one
who's enjoying this!

759
00:45:45,075 --> 00:45:46,744
I'll be struggling when I get pregnant!

760
00:45:46,827 --> 00:45:48,287
I also need to be happy.

761
00:45:48,370 --> 00:45:50,706
Well, your happiness is such a turnoff!

762
00:45:50,789 --> 00:45:52,374
-Wait.
-[Chiqui] What, really?

763
00:45:52,458 --> 00:45:54,835
-I can't do this.
-Hey!

764
00:45:54,918 --> 00:45:57,546
-[upbeat music playing]
-[Samuel yelps]

765
00:45:59,173 --> 00:46:01,008
I'm ready now, Chiqui!

766
00:46:01,925 --> 00:46:03,427
[groans]

767
00:46:09,308 --> 00:46:10,893
-Chiqui?
-[growls]

768
00:46:13,479 --> 00:46:16,190
-[Samuel screams]
-[door closes]

769
00:46:18,442 --> 00:46:20,360
I'm so tired.

770
00:46:22,488 --> 00:46:24,865
Chiqui, I'm so tired.

771
00:46:25,449 --> 00:46:30,496
[crying] So, so tired.

772
00:46:34,249 --> 00:46:35,167
Wait.

773
00:46:36,043 --> 00:46:37,753
I'm so tired.

774
00:46:38,879 --> 00:46:42,257
[sobbing incoherently]

775
00:46:42,341 --> 00:46:44,384
[Chiqui murmuring soothingly]

776
00:46:44,468 --> 00:46:47,596
[sobbing continues]

777
00:46:59,191 --> 00:47:00,234
Samuel.

778
00:47:05,072 --> 00:47:08,450
If you can't do it, don't force yourself.

779
00:47:09,326 --> 00:47:10,202
What?

780
00:47:10,994 --> 00:47:14,748
Idiot. These are tears of joy.

781
00:47:16,667 --> 00:47:20,212
I almost threw up, but...

782
00:47:21,380 --> 00:47:22,714
I did it!

783
00:47:23,257 --> 00:47:24,883
[laughs]

784
00:47:24,967 --> 00:47:26,510
-Success.
-Congrats!

785
00:47:35,894 --> 00:47:39,856
Remember, you have to act surprised.

786
00:47:41,692 --> 00:47:46,864
-[all] Happy birthday!
-[guests clapping and cheering]

787
00:47:46,947 --> 00:47:49,324
Wow!

