01:01:32,230 --> 01:01:34,023
Did you think you could fool me?

1050
01:01:35,483 --> 01:01:37,151
You, too, Gabriel.

1051
01:01:38,277 --> 01:01:40,071
I wasn't trying to deceive you.

1052
01:01:40,154 --> 01:01:43,449
Then why does this show
that you're not the father of Kat's baby?

1053
01:01:43,533 --> 01:01:46,160
-Let me explain--
-You don't have to explain!

1054
01:01:49,455 --> 01:01:52,583
[Don Emilio] I can't believe
my legitimate children tried to trick me.

1055
01:01:56,879 --> 01:01:58,005
Samuel...

1056
01:01:59,715 --> 01:02:01,801
you made me very proud.

1057
01:02:03,803 --> 01:02:07,640
There is no doubt
that Chiqui is carrying a Panti.

1058
01:02:07,724 --> 01:02:09,600
-[Samuel gasps]
-[Vilma shrieks]

1059
01:02:10,560 --> 01:02:12,353
That's my son!

1060
01:02:12,437 --> 01:02:14,147
Way to go!

1061
01:02:14,230 --> 01:02:16,733
[both laughing]

1062
01:02:24,907 --> 01:02:26,159
[Nora sighs]

1063
01:02:31,789 --> 01:02:32,915
Let's go, Mom.

1064
01:02:41,674 --> 01:02:44,719
Another crazy stunt? Why are you leaving?

1065
01:02:44,802 --> 01:02:47,180
I'm leaving, Don Emilio.

1066
01:02:48,473 --> 01:02:50,433
I can't stand you anymore.

1067
01:02:50,516 --> 01:02:52,977
You're too dramatic, Nora!

1068
01:02:53,853 --> 01:02:55,062
Am I throwing you out?

1069
01:02:55,146 --> 01:02:57,273
I don't take it personally.

1070
01:02:57,982 --> 01:03:00,526
After all, 100,000,000 is 100,000,000.

1071
01:03:01,527 --> 01:03:05,823
A person's true colors will
show whenever money is involved.

1072
01:03:06,991 --> 01:03:08,951
The game is far from over.

1073
01:03:09,035 --> 01:03:12,538
You may still get any woman pregnant.

1074
01:03:14,791 --> 01:03:15,791
Don Emilio--

1075
01:03:15,875 --> 01:03:17,877
Excuse me, sir.

1076
01:03:17,960 --> 01:03:20,254
It's true, we all want the money.

1077
01:03:20,338 --> 01:03:22,298
But if you were more sensitive,

1078
01:03:22,381 --> 01:03:26,677
you'd know that's not all they want.

1079
01:03:26,761 --> 01:03:27,762
[Kat] That's right.

1080
01:03:27,845 --> 01:03:32,850
They want your love.

1081
01:03:32,934 --> 01:03:35,436
[laughs]

1082
01:03:35,520 --> 01:03:38,314
You've got some nerve to answer back.

1083
01:03:38,397 --> 01:03:41,692
You are all opportunists.

1084
01:03:41,776 --> 01:03:42,818
Yes.

1085
01:03:43,778 --> 01:03:45,905
We were blinded by your wealth...

1086
01:03:47,490 --> 01:03:49,242
but not anymore.

1087
01:03:49,325 --> 01:03:50,451
We have come to our senses.

1088
01:03:51,494 --> 01:03:52,495
This is wrong.

1089
01:03:53,162 --> 01:03:54,956
[speaking Tagalog]

1090
01:03:55,039 --> 01:04:00,461
[speaking Tagalog]

1091
01:04:00,545 --> 01:04:02,004
In English...

1092
01:04:02,713 --> 01:04:04,507
"That unhatched offspring

1093
01:04:04,590 --> 01:04:07,134
is not a product of love...

1094
01:04:07,218 --> 01:04:08,469
but of need!"

1095
01:04:10,888 --> 01:04:12,557
[in Tagalog] Did he have to translate?

1096
01:04:13,891 --> 01:04:16,894
Want me to translate for you?
I can do it in whale language.

1097
01:04:16,978 --> 01:04:19,230
[imitating whale]

1098
01:04:20,064 --> 01:04:20,898
Let's go.

1099
01:04:23,568 --> 01:04:25,361
Uh, Nora!

1100
01:04:26,279 --> 01:04:30,700
You left this in your old room
which is now my room.

1101
01:04:32,743 --> 01:04:34,704
This isn't mine.

1102
01:04:34,787 --> 01:04:37,957
I don't own anything fake.

1103
01:04:39,667 --> 01:04:41,460
Oh, it is mine.

1104
01:04:42,336 --> 01:04:45,172
Actually, everything's mine now.

1105
01:04:45,256 --> 01:04:48,092
I am now number one.

1106
01:04:48,759 --> 01:04:51,512
You are still number two, Vilma.

1107
01:04:52,638 --> 01:04:57,935
I was never number one in Emilio's life.

1108
01:04:58,644 --> 01:05:01,606
His number one is none other than himself.

1109
01:05:04,609 --> 01:05:07,320
I wish the two of you good luck.

1110
01:05:07,403 --> 01:05:08,321
[scoffs]

1111
01:05:09,447 --> 01:05:10,740
Bitter!

1112
01:05:11,282 --> 01:05:12,950
B-T-T-ER.

1113
01:05:13,618 --> 01:05:15,161
Bitter!

1114
01:05:15,244 --> 01:05:17,747
[Samuel laughing]

1115
01:05:17,830 --> 01:05:18,998
[Samuel] Estong!

1116
01:05:22,376 --> 01:05:24,920
[Samuel giggling]

1117
01:05:29,634 --> 01:05:32,094
[Estong] Bella!

1118
01:05:32,803 --> 01:05:35,514
[Samuel] No, Edward, please!

1119
01:05:35,598 --> 01:05:39,018
-Come here!
-[laughing]

1120
01:05:41,938 --> 01:05:43,356
Bella!

1121
01:05:49,278 --> 01:05:50,488
[Samuel moaning]

1122
01:05:53,658 --> 01:05:56,077
[Samuel and Estong laughing]

1123
01:05:58,704 --> 01:06:01,248
[slurring] I'm not drunk. I want more.

1124
01:06:01,332 --> 01:06:02,625
Come on. Please.

1125
01:06:02,708 --> 01:06:05,211
-Promise?
-Just one more.

1126
01:06:05,294 --> 01:06:08,464
-Are you sure?
-Yes! One more!

1127
01:06:08,547 --> 01:06:11,133
-Okay, wait.
-I can handle it.

1128
01:06:11,217 --> 01:06:13,386
I can.

1129
01:06:14,887 --> 01:06:16,639
[Nora snoring]

1130
01:06:17,765 --> 01:06:18,683
Look at her.

1131
01:06:24,313 --> 01:06:25,648
And she says she's not drunk.

1132
01:06:38,869 --> 01:06:39,870
[door opens]

1133
01:06:42,248 --> 01:06:43,165
[door closes]

1134
01:06:47,336 --> 01:06:48,838
Uh...

1135
01:06:49,505 --> 01:06:51,716
[stutters] Where's Daniel?

1136
01:06:52,717 --> 01:06:56,887
Uh, she brought Joy to the bus terminal.

1137
01:07:00,558 --> 01:07:03,561
Where is Joy going?

1138
01:07:04,478 --> 01:07:07,565
To their province.

1139
01:07:17,074 --> 01:07:21,120
[sensual guitar music playing]

1140
01:07:43,059 --> 01:07:44,894
Are you seducing me?

1141
01:07:44,977 --> 01:07:47,146
-[music stops suddenly]
-What?

1142
01:07:48,939 --> 01:07:51,484
No. Nothing.

1143
01:07:52,318 --> 01:07:53,736
I think I'm drunk.

1144
01:07:56,280 --> 01:07:57,865
Why would I seduce you?

1145
01:07:59,575 --> 01:08:01,160
I love your brother.

1146
01:08:02,578 --> 01:08:05,664
No need to emphasize. I've accepted that.

1147
01:08:07,333 --> 01:08:09,001
You grew tired of me.

1148
01:08:09,585 --> 01:08:11,128
It happens.

1149
01:08:13,422 --> 01:08:15,841
Wait, wait, wait. I grew tired of you?

1150
01:08:16,926 --> 01:08:18,511
What are you talking about?

1151
01:08:18,594 --> 01:08:19,929
That's not true.

1152
01:08:20,763 --> 01:08:22,807
You had no time for me.

1153
01:08:23,516 --> 01:08:25,684
You had gig after gig.

1154
01:08:26,811 --> 01:08:29,104
You loved your work
more than you loved me.

1155
01:08:29,188 --> 01:08:31,816
I was doing it for us.

1156
01:08:34,109 --> 01:08:36,779
Even on my birthday, huh?

1157
01:08:38,697 --> 01:08:42,576
When I came home that day,
huh, where were you?

1158
01:08:42,660 --> 01:08:45,204
But Daniel was there.

1159
01:08:45,704 --> 01:08:47,039
He even made the dish

1160
01:08:47,122 --> 01:08:49,416
that I always asked you to cook for me.

1161
01:08:49,500 --> 01:08:51,377
Frog stew.

1162
01:08:54,713 --> 01:08:56,298
I have to admit...

1163
01:08:57,299 --> 01:09:00,177
because of that dish...

1164
01:09:00,261 --> 01:09:01,470
I fell for him.

1165
01:09:01,554 --> 01:09:02,680
Excuse me!

1166
01:09:04,056 --> 01:09:06,225
That's my frog stew.

1167
01:09:07,685 --> 01:09:09,478
Before I left for work,

1168
01:09:09,562 --> 01:09:11,146
I made sure to catch some frogs

1169
01:09:11,230 --> 01:09:13,566
so I could cook your favorite dish.

1170
01:09:13,649 --> 01:09:17,486
Hey, Chiqui. What's your problem?
Why are you leaving?

1171
01:09:17,570 --> 01:09:19,822
There's no place for drama here!

1172
01:09:20,406 --> 01:09:24,118
Samuel, did you get me pregnant
because you needed it?

1173
01:09:24,201 --> 01:09:25,995
Or do you need me, so you got me pregnant?

1174
01:09:26,078 --> 01:09:28,330
What? I don't get it, babe.

1175
01:09:28,414 --> 01:09:30,374
I saw you with Estong last night.

1176
01:09:30,457 --> 01:09:32,835
If you wanted it,
why didn't you come to me?

1177
01:09:32,918 --> 01:09:34,253
Why did you have to go to him?

1178
01:09:34,336 --> 01:09:36,130
Do you like him? Do you love him?

1179
01:09:36,213 --> 01:09:37,840
Chiqui, look here.

1180
01:09:37,923 --> 01:09:40,968
First of all, I didn't ask for it.

1181
01:09:41,051 --> 01:09:42,511
Estong did.

1182
01:09:43,137 --> 01:09:44,513
Second, I don't love him.

1183
01:09:45,556 --> 01:09:47,099
Not yet.

1184
01:09:47,182 --> 01:09:49,643
You ask too many questions.
You're messing with my life.

1185
01:09:49,727 --> 01:09:51,645
Why shouldn't I? What are we?

1186
01:09:51,729 --> 01:09:53,772
Business partners.

1187
01:09:54,732 --> 01:09:57,359
We're partners and it's not just business.

1188
01:09:57,443 --> 01:09:59,945
Oh, are you requiring me to love you?

1189
01:10:00,029 --> 01:10:02,489
If you want me to see this through,

1190
01:10:02,573 --> 01:10:03,824
you have to become a lesbian.

1191
01:10:03,908 --> 01:10:06,619
Stop seeing Estong.
I don't want to share you.

1192
01:10:06,702 --> 01:10:08,704
Chiqui, you're not sharing me,

1193
01:10:08,787 --> 01:10:11,707
because we were never a couple
and we'll never be together.

1194
01:10:11,790 --> 01:10:12,917
I hope you know that.

1195
01:10:13,626 --> 01:10:14,627
If we're not together,

1196
01:10:14,710 --> 01:10:17,546
then there's no reason to push
through with this pregnancy.

1197
01:10:17,630 --> 01:10:19,673
What are you saying?
You'll get an abortion?

1198
01:10:19,757 --> 01:10:21,091
Where's your conscience?

1199
01:10:21,175 --> 01:10:22,551
Did your conscience bother you

1200
01:10:22,635 --> 01:10:25,137
when you knocked up someone
you don't love?

1201
01:10:25,220 --> 01:10:27,640
It's my body, my decision.

1202
01:10:27,723 --> 01:10:30,392
-I will get an abortion.
-Chiqui, Chiqui!

1203
01:10:30,476 --> 01:10:34,647
-Hey! I'm leaving!
-Don't leave! Chiqui, please.

1204
01:10:34,730 --> 01:10:38,484
-Don't interfere! I'm going!
-You're not leaving.

1205
01:10:38,567 --> 01:10:40,694
-Chiqui! I'm sorry.
-[grunts]

1206
01:10:40,778 --> 01:10:43,697
-[groans]
-Sorry, sorry, sorry.

1207
01:10:46,075 --> 01:10:48,994
-[groans]
-Oh, my God.

1208
01:10:49,536 --> 01:10:52,539
Help! Help!

1209
01:10:52,623 --> 01:10:53,707
Chiqui, sorry.

1210
01:10:57,795 --> 01:10:59,797
What took you so long?

1211
01:11:02,424 --> 01:11:04,677
I thought you were just bringing Joy home.

1212
01:11:05,803 --> 01:11:07,846
I went to church.

1213
01:11:07,930 --> 01:11:09,932
I asked for a sign from God

1214
01:11:10,015 --> 01:11:13,852
if I should pursue getting
my inheritance from Don Emilio.

1215
01:11:13,936 --> 01:11:18,148
[chuckles] That was some novena,
to last all night!

1216
01:11:20,484 --> 01:11:22,486
I hope you asked for forgiveness from God.

1217
01:11:23,904 --> 01:11:24,738
Forgiveness?

1218
01:11:25,906 --> 01:11:27,408
For stealing Zernan!

1219
01:11:27,992 --> 01:11:29,118
Huh?

1220
01:11:29,201 --> 01:11:33,247
I thought you had moved on.
I thought we were okay.

1221
01:11:33,831 --> 01:11:35,416
I thought so, too.

1222
01:11:37,960 --> 01:11:39,712
I really believed that...

1223
01:11:41,005 --> 01:11:43,215
Zernan fell for you.

1224
01:11:44,800 --> 01:11:46,510
But you're something else.

1225
01:11:47,928 --> 01:11:50,180
You were sneaky. You stole him from me.

1226
01:11:52,349 --> 01:11:57,479
You even pretended
that you cooked my frog stew.

1227
01:11:57,563 --> 01:12:00,149
My God! Why fight about him now?

1228
01:12:00,232 --> 01:12:02,818
-Do you still like him?
-No.

1229
01:12:02,901 --> 01:12:06,155
Oh, then what's the issue?

1230
01:12:06,238 --> 01:12:07,990
The issue is, you lied to me.

1231
01:12:08,073 --> 01:12:10,075
And you haven't apologized until now.

1232
01:12:10,159 --> 01:12:11,827
Why should I say sorry?

1233
01:12:12,328 --> 01:12:15,748
Did you say sorry
when you left me with Don Emilio?

1234
01:12:15,831 --> 01:12:17,666
I'll give you what you're asking for, huh?

1235
01:12:17,750 --> 01:12:20,919
-What if I do that to your face?
-[both grunting]

1236
01:12:21,628 --> 01:12:23,297
[Nora] Hey, hey!

1237
01:12:24,631 --> 01:12:26,467
Stop that!

1238
01:12:26,550 --> 01:12:29,136
What's the matter with you?
Fighting at such an early hour.

1239
01:12:29,219 --> 01:12:30,929
You're acting like children!

1240
01:12:31,013 --> 01:12:32,723
Don Emilio called...

1241
01:12:33,265 --> 01:12:34,600
asking me to come back.

1242
01:12:35,642 --> 01:12:36,894
And you will?

1243
01:12:36,977 --> 01:12:39,438
He's all alone there.
No one's taking care of him.

1244
01:12:39,521 --> 01:12:41,440
Samuel rushed to the hospital

1245
01:12:41,523 --> 01:12:43,734
because Chiqui had a miscarriage.

1246
01:12:43,817 --> 01:12:47,237
[sober music playing]

1247
01:12:55,537 --> 01:12:57,748
[nurse] Sir, please go back to the room.

1248
01:12:57,831 --> 01:13:00,042
We'll just bring her there.

1249
01:13:12,554 --> 01:13:13,972
Don't be so sad.

1250
01:13:14,056 --> 01:13:15,557
According to the doctor,

1251
01:13:15,641 --> 01:13:18,811
Chiqui can get pregnant again
in six weeks.

1252
01:13:20,187 --> 01:13:21,480
Are you serious?

1253
01:13:22,773 --> 01:13:26,026
She's not yet well, and you're already
thinking of getting her pregnant.

1254
01:13:26,110 --> 01:13:30,781
Why were you fighting?
Were you fooling around with a man again?

1255
01:13:31,824 --> 01:13:33,867
You know how much Chiqui's into you,

1256
01:13:33,951 --> 01:13:36,286
and yet you are still flirting
with other men.

1257
01:13:36,370 --> 01:13:38,705
Couldn't you wait
for the child to come out?

1258
01:13:38,789 --> 01:13:40,666
We could have had 300,000,000.

1259
01:13:40,749 --> 01:13:42,918
-And now it's gone.
-Mom!

1260
01:13:44,920 --> 01:13:46,213
Mom, give me a break.

1261
01:13:47,965 --> 01:13:49,758
You lost a grandchild.

1262
01:13:50,342 --> 01:13:51,844
I lost a child.

1263
01:13:56,515 --> 01:13:58,016
If I were a good person,

1264
01:13:58,100 --> 01:14:00,185
I wouldn't have dragged her into this.

1265
01:14:01,019 --> 01:14:02,354
[sighs]

1266
01:14:03,188 --> 01:14:05,274
You can be a good person

1267
01:14:05,357 --> 01:14:07,484
while you are waiting to become rich.

1268
01:14:07,568 --> 01:14:09,611
Just take a look at some politicians. See?

1269
01:14:09,695 --> 01:14:13,782
They hoard the people's money
before they share their blessings.

1270
01:14:13,866 --> 01:14:16,618
Who knows?
You might become a senator someday.

1271
01:14:16,702 --> 01:14:21,915
We need your inheritance first
so that you can become,

1272
01:14:21,999 --> 01:14:25,878
as I promised, a total woman.

1273
01:14:25,961 --> 01:14:27,838
Will you trade that for your conscience?

1274
01:14:30,716 --> 01:14:33,469
Shouldn't I want to be a good person

1275
01:14:34,303 --> 01:14:36,346
rather than be a total woman?

1276
01:14:48,400 --> 01:14:49,985
What are you doing here?

1277
01:14:50,068 --> 01:14:51,653
[inhales deeply]

1278
01:14:52,404 --> 01:14:53,906
We heard...

1279
01:14:55,199 --> 01:14:57,409
We're all not getting our inheritance.

1280
01:14:58,702 --> 01:14:59,578
Happy?

1281
01:14:59,661 --> 01:15:02,414
I told you he'd be mean.

1282
01:15:02,497 --> 01:15:05,042
We're just wasting our time. Let's go.

1283
01:15:05,125 --> 01:15:07,753
We're just making sure
you're okay, Samuel.

1284
01:15:09,588 --> 01:15:12,216
Only a Panti can comfort another Panti.

1285
01:15:13,425 --> 01:15:15,886
-[sentimental music playing]
-We may have misunderstandings...

1286
01:15:18,555 --> 01:15:20,349
but in the end, we are all Pantis.

1287
01:15:24,770 --> 01:15:26,772
Why so big?

1288
01:15:26,855 --> 01:15:28,190
It looks stupid.

1289
01:15:31,610 --> 01:15:33,612
[all chuckle]

1290
01:15:34,821 --> 01:15:36,114
It's her fault.

1291
01:15:36,198 --> 01:15:38,700
I told her you're not a typhoon victim,

1292
01:15:38,784 --> 01:15:40,911
but she still brought relief goods.

1293
01:15:40,994 --> 01:15:42,996
-[chuckles]
-At least it's assorted.

1294
01:15:43,080 --> 01:15:44,998
[laughs] There's a lot to try.

1295
01:15:45,082 --> 01:15:46,959
[sniffles] Thank you.

1296
01:15:47,042 --> 01:15:49,670
Thank you, um... forgive me.

1297
01:15:50,629 --> 01:15:52,589
I'm just so confused.

1298
01:15:53,799 --> 01:15:55,050
[Don Emilio] Samuel!

1299
01:15:59,054 --> 01:16:01,890
Why is nobody telling me

1300
01:16:01,974 --> 01:16:04,476
how my grandchild is doing?

1301
01:16:11,358 --> 01:16:14,778
-Chiqui had a miscarriage.
-Oh?

1302
01:16:15,904 --> 01:16:17,698
So, it's all even again.

1303
01:16:19,157 --> 01:16:20,742
I will wait for all of you at home.

1304
01:16:22,327 --> 01:16:23,704
[Samuel] Wait.

1305
01:16:24,288 --> 01:16:26,415
Is that all you can say, huh?

1306
01:16:28,083 --> 01:16:30,210
You're not going to ask how I am?

